WEBVTT

00:02.517 --> 00:04.553
If I could describe my dad in one word, it would be strong.

00:04.909 --> 00:05.884
Responsible.

00:06.001 --> 00:06.818
Inspirational.

00:07.397 --> 00:08.028
Fun.

00:08.383 --> 00:09.261
Predictable.

00:10.046 --> 00:12.597
I'm not just his son, we're friends.

00:13.277 --> 00:15.363
They have a joy for life that's unmatched.

00:15.625 --> 00:18.362
Marshmallows? What?

00:18.776 --> 00:19.992
He loves me.

00:21.685 --> 00:24.235
I am who I am because of him.

00:24.728 --> 00:25.475
I love my dad.

